{
  "video_id": "F9qF6FvwrHI",
  "title": "How Nations Make Up National Identities | NYT - The Interpreter",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 790.0,
      "end_time": 3835.0,
      "text": "Nationality feels so powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3835.0,
      "end_time": 6140.0,
      "text": "We fight for our country."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6140.0,
      "end_time": 7550.0,
      "text": "We cheer for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7550.0,
      "end_time": 9140.0,
      "text": "We draw our values from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9140.0,
      "end_time": 11900.0,
      "text": "It’s a big way many of us describe who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11900.0,
      "end_time": 13630.0,
      "text": "but it didn’t used to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13630.0,
      "end_time": 16630.0,
      "text": "Up until really recently, our identities came from stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16630.0,
      "end_time": 18220.0,
      "text": "immediately around us —"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 18220.0,
      "end_time": 20860.0,
      "text": "clans, religion, family."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 20860.0,
      "end_time": 22450.0,
      "text": "If you think about it, nationality"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22450.0,
      "end_time": 24669.0,
      "text": "is weird, the idea that you identify"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24670.0,
      "end_time": 27430.0,
      "text": "with millions of strangers just based on borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27430.0,
      "end_time": 30476.0,
      "text": "That’s because national identity is made up."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34444.0,
      "end_time": 35232.0,
      "text": "“U.S.A.!"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 35232.0,
      "end_time": 36320.0,
      "text": "U.S.A.!”"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36320.0,
      "end_time": 37916.0,
      "text": "“And then [INAUDIBLE] scores!”"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39910.0,
      "end_time": 43150.0,
      "text": "National identity is the myth that built the modern world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43150.0,
      "end_time": 47870.0,
      "text": "but it also primes us for dictatorship, racism, genocide."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 47870.0,
      "end_time": 49930.0,
      "text": "And today, we’re fighting over whether to keep"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49930.0,
      "end_time": 51800.0,
      "text": "that kind of national identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51800.0,
      "end_time": 55154.0,
      "text": "To understand why, you have to see how new this idea is."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58600.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "So you think you know what France is."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60160.0,
      "end_time": 62800.0,
      "text": "It’s a place united by the French language"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62800.0,
      "end_time": 64209.0,
      "text": "and the French ethnicity, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 64209.0,
      "end_time": 66580.0,
      "text": "But as of the French Revolution, half of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66580.0,
      "end_time": 68170.0,
      "text": "there could not speak French."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 68170.0,
      "end_time": 69910.0,
      "text": "Only one in eight spoke it well."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 69910.0,
      "end_time": 71800.0,
      "text": "These are the languages that people spoke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71800.0,
      "end_time": 74679.0,
      "text": "just a patchwork that didn’t line up with borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74680.0,
      "end_time": 77350.0,
      "text": "We know from modern genetics that ethnicity didn’t line up"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 77350.0,
      "end_time": 79119.0,
      "text": "with borders, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79120.0,
      "end_time": 80590.0,
      "text": "National identity became the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80590.0,
      "end_time": 85900.0,
      "text": "that language, race, and borders should add up to a country."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 85900.0,
      "end_time": 87100.0,
      "text": "Nations can’t admit they’re made up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87100.0,
      "end_time": 88810.0,
      "text": "so they invent a national mythology"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 88810.0,
      "end_time": 91250.0,
      "text": "that says they’ve been like this forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96360.0,
      "end_time": 98179.0,
      "text": "The modern era brought four big changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98180.0,
      "end_time": 100400.0,
      "text": "that led to national identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101750.0,
      "end_time": 104640.0,
      "text": "People moved in big numbers from the country to the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104640.0,
      "end_time": 106480.0,
      "text": "and they needed a common language."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 106480.0,
      "end_time": 108435.0,
      "text": "New technology, like newspapers and trains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 108435.0,
      "end_time": 110601.0,
      "text": "made countries feel smaller and more interconnected."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111760.0,
      "end_time": 114794.0,
      "text": "War was changing into this vast all-consuming thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114794.0,
      "end_time": 116210.0,
      "text": "Countries needed people that cared"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116210.0,
      "end_time": 117699.0,
      "text": "so much about their nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 117700.0,
      "end_time": 119675.0,
      "text": "they’d fight for it in huge numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 120980.0,
      "end_time": 123650.0,
      "text": "Governments were challenging religion for power."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 123650.0,
      "end_time": 125780.0,
      "text": "Here’s Napoleon taking his crown from the pope"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 125780.0,
      "end_time": 126980.0,
      "text": "to crown himself emperor."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 126980.0,
      "end_time": 127936.0,
      "text": "It was a big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129830.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133420.0,
      "text": "These four things sparked an era of revolutions in democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 133420.0,
      "end_time": 136369.0,
      "text": "but they also unleashed ideas of nationalism, militarism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 136370.0,
      "end_time": 137780.0,
      "text": "and leader worship."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137780.0,
      "end_time": 139280.0,
      "text": "People came to see their countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 139280.0,
      "end_time": 141710.0,
      "text": "as extensions of themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141710.0,
      "end_time": 144500.0,
      "text": "This new identity meant that a nation got its authority,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144500.0,
      "end_time": 147170.0,
      "text": "not from the government, or the King, or God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 147170.0,
      "end_time": 148790.0,
      "text": "but from the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148790.0,
      "end_time": 152792.0,
      "text": "This changed the world, but it also changed how we think."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 155560.0,
      "end_time": 158380.0,
      "text": "National identity changes our reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 158380.0,
      "end_time": 160720.0,
      "text": "We experience whatever happens to our nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160720.0,
      "end_time": 162327.0,
      "text": "as if it happened to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 163730.0,
      "end_time": 166549.0,
      "text": "“Rocky IV” can tell us a lot about what national identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166550.0,
      "end_time": 167390.0,
      "text": "does to our brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 167390.0,
      "end_time": 169670.0,
      "text": "“The Russian towers above the American.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169670.0,
      "end_time": 172760.0,
      "text": "A 1994 study tested the attitudes of Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 172760.0,
      "end_time": 173660.0,
      "text": "watching the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 173660.0,
      "end_time": 176430.0,
      "text": "It includes an amazing footnote."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176430.0,
      "end_time": 179720.0,
      "text": "All 216 participants were women because, quote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 179720.0,
      "end_time": 182200.0,
      "text": "“There were no males who had not seen ‘Rocky IV.’”"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 182200.0,
      "end_time": 183700.0,
      "text": "Anyway —"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186316.0,
      "end_time": 188270.0,
      "text": "When Rocky beat his Russian opponent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188270.0,
      "end_time": 190890.0,
      "text": "participants who strongly identified as American"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190890.0,
      "end_time": 192908.0,
      "text": "felt a boost in self-esteem."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 195900.0,
      "end_time": 197610.0,
      "text": "When they were shown re-edited footage"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197610.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "to make it look like Rocky lost, they felt a drop in self-esteem"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "and they became likelier to hold negative views about Russians."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207359.0,
      "text": "But when they said something bad about Russians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207360.0,
      "end_time": 210680.0,
      "text": "their self-esteem recovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210680.0,
      "end_time": 212380.0,
      "text": "When we feel threatened, it makes"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212380.0,
      "end_time": 215730.0,
      "text": "us want to humiliate and dominate the outsider."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 215730.0,
      "end_time": 219700.0,
      "text": "That dynamic doesn’t just apply to individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219700.0,
      "end_time": 222300.0,
      "text": "It can apply to whole societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 222300.0,
      "end_time": 224559.0,
      "text": "This can drive war, itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 224560.0,
      "end_time": 226870.0,
      "text": "One study found that any country whose team"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 226870.0,
      "end_time": 229330.0,
      "text": "plays in the World Cup becomes likelier"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 229330.0,
      "end_time": 231560.0,
      "text": "to launch attacks abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 231560.0,
      "end_time": 234710.0,
      "text": "That hostility also plays out against minorities and migrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234710.0,
      "end_time": 237470.0,
      "text": "who don’t fit the national myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 237470.0,
      "end_time": 241220.0,
      "text": "It only took a century for these problems of modern nationalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 241220.0,
      "end_time": 244570.0,
      "text": "to culminate into World War II,  something so terrible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 244570.0,
      "end_time": 251274.0,
      "text": "it convinced the world to try a new kind of national identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 251274.0,
      "end_time": 255474.0,
      "text": "“Great American melting pot.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255474.0,
      "end_time": 258630.0,
      "text": "This model of identity is based on an idea from the United"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 258630.0,
      "end_time": 259649.0,
      "text": "States."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 259649.0,
      "end_time": 262200.0,
      "text": "Anyone can be American if you share values"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 262200.0,
      "end_time": 263940.0,
      "text": "like freedom and hard work."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 263940.0,
      "end_time": 266480.0,
      "text": "“May I please remind you that it does not say"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 266480.0,
      "end_time": 269616.0,
      "text": "RSVP on the Statue of Liberty.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 270370.0,
      "end_time": 273540.0,
      "text": "It’s a stirring idea, but it never completely worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 273540.0,
      "end_time": 276115.0,
      "text": "“Your race is your nation.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 276115.0,
      "end_time": 279510.0,
      "text": "“If you don’t speak English and don’t contribute, get out!”"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279510.0,
      "end_time": 281730.0,
      "text": "The belief that being American is really"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 281730.0,
      "end_time": 283650.0,
      "text": "about race, religion, and language"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283650.0,
      "end_time": 285419.0,
      "text": "also runs throughout history."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 285420.0,
      "end_time": 287250.0,
      "text": "So what makes a country?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287250.0,
      "end_time": 289800.0,
      "text": "Which identity should matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 289800.0,
      "end_time": 292620.0,
      "text": "That fight defines so much of the world right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 292620.0,
      "end_time": 294270.0,
      "text": "And it’s intensified."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294270.0,
      "end_time": 296609.0,
      "text": "You see it in the backlash to the European Union."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296610.0,
      "end_time": 298320.0,
      "text": "“We’ve got our country back.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 298320.0,
      "end_time": 301300.0,
      "text": "You see it in how Donald Trump began his campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301300.0,
      "end_time": 302849.0,
      "text": "“We either have a country or we don’t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 302850.0,
      "end_time": 303750.0,
      "text": "and it’s that simple.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 303750.0,
      "end_time": 306400.0,
      "text": "The national myth is powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 306400.0,
      "end_time": 308940.0,
      "text": "We fight for a common past and a common future."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 308940.0,
      "end_time": 314630.0,
      "text": "It isn’t real, but that doesn’t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314630.0,
      "end_time": 318400.0,
      "text": "We’ve been taught for so long that this is who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318400.0,
      "end_time": 320500.0,
      "text": "Building a world based on shared values"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320500.0,
      "end_time": 322920.0,
      "text": "really means creating a new myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322920.0,
      "end_time": 326200.0,
      "text": "But that only works if it feels as powerful as the last one."
    }
  ]
}